snippet.title: Drive.RS: Open World Racing - Trailer - iOS and Android - Race Drift Free Roam Game
snippet.description:
Available for pre-register now on Android and iOS  :)

iOS pre-order 
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/drive-rs-open-world-racing/id1613239648

Android - Google Play pre-register
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rumblesushi.drivers

** If you have problems finding it on Google Play in your country, try putting "rumblesushi" or "drive.rs"  with the " " around it, exactly as I put here

On the app store it should show for Drive.Rs or Rumblesushi
